"{\"uid\": \"baptistnews.com-article-evangelicals-upset-about-the-olympics-are-pearl-clutching-hypocrites\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"OpinionSusan M. Shaw, Senior Columnist|\\u00a0 July 27, 2024  Enough with the pearl-clutching!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 88, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.89166896651721e-18, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As if many rightwing Christians have nothing better to do, on Friday they set X alight with outrage over a scene from the Paris Olympics opening celebration.\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drag queens were part of a DaVinci's Last Supper pose, oh my!\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5228174833271315e-26, \"text\": \"DaVinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.449793572377298e-28, \"text\": \"Last Supper\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Susan Shaw  So with their acute provincial snowflake watchfulness for any perceived slight and no sense of diverse cultural sensibilities, the pearl-clutchers castigated the Olympics and the French for \\\"mocking\\\" Christianity.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.998191473072026, \"rank\": 0.0018112150197392787, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 4.821257331944368e-12, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never mind that their Bible-hawking, adulterous, authoritarian, convicted felon of a presidential candidate says he never has asked for forgiveness.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Drag queens in a Last Supper pose is what Christians really need to worry about.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hypocrisy stinks to high heaven.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, why would we expect anything different from average pew sitters when conservative leaders like Nikki Haley and JD Vance have made their own Faustian bargains with the Donald?\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Haley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikki Haley\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Haley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Haley\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"score\": 0.9999997620248279, \"rank\": 2.37805976913166e-07, \"text\": \"JD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\"}, {\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999968648980061, \"rank\": 3.13511189099324e-06, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"score\": 0.9935135521394337, \"rank\": 0.006527127506097285, \"text\": \"Faustian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's unfit to serve, they say, until, of course, they need him to have access to their own share of political power.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The hypocrisy stinks to high heaven.\\\"\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not that drag queensat the Olympics is the only instance of right-wing pearl-clutching of late.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just look at the angst female pastors have caused among Southern Baptists, and I am not talking about women as senior pastors.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.828991358768769e-21, \"text\": \"Southern Baptists\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even women serving aschildren'spastors are causing people like Al Mohler and Mike Law to reach for their pearls.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Mohler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Al Mohler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Mohler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Mohler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now, God forbid, we have a woman - a Black and Indian woman, no less - running for president of the United States of America!\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998897411168258, \"rank\": 0.00010799137843288269, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cue the racism and misogyny.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Never mind she's a Baptist, a Christian, a lifelong public servant.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"score\": 0.9790338702261326, \"rank\": 0.02140486000940716, \"text\": \"Baptist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\"}, {\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999933091704507, \"rank\": 6.690874199898789e-06, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, JD Vance may soon learn that crossing childless cat ladies is not such a good idea.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"score\": 0.9999997620248279, \"rank\": 2.37805976913166e-07, \"text\": \"JD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\"}, {\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999968648980061, \"rank\": 3.13511189099324e-06, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not clutch pearls.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We fill out ballots, donate and campaign.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Right has gone so far as to mockKamala Harris' laugh, but maybe it's time we had a littlejoie de vivrein the White House.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How much better to dance in Converse sneakers than incite insurrection with a tweet.\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Taylor_All-Stars\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Converse sneakers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Taylor_All-Stars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Taylor_All-Stars\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as for drag queens in Paris, if some of these folks actually bothered to study history, they'd learn there is a rich tradition of sacred clowns whose role is to make fun of our most sacred traditions so we do not take ourselves too seriously.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999972484262456, \"rank\": 2.7515812024363645e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, if they bothered to read the Bible with a little more scholarship at hand, they'd also discover that, at points, it's hilarious, and Jesus himself was not above cracking jokes and using a little well-timed sarcasm.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999159758808, \"rank\": 8.402430618153063e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be the first to admit this pieceis a bit snarkier than most of my pleas for sanity and good will among Christians, but I am finding it exasperating and hard to take seriously all the pearl-clutching, defensiveness, hypocrisy and meanness of people who call themselves Christians and act anything but Christ-like.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They give the rest of us a bad name.\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Surely, there are more important things for Christians to do in the world than worry about drag queens, although you would not know that from the legislation in a number of red states.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What if Christians spent their timeactually doing the things Jesus said God's people ought to do, like feeding the hungry, clothing the naked, making peace and loving our neighbors?\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3163, \"end\": 3168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999159758808, \"rank\": 8.402430618153063e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know we progressives have to take the pearl-clutchers seriously, though, because we have seen what they do when they are in power.\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Project 2025 lays out such a dystopian vision thatThe Handmaid's Taleseems child's play.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a process theologian, I believe God is at work in every particle of the universe, calling it to achieve its divine aim, and so we can not give up on those who clutch their pearls and often throw them before swine.\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And we can not simply call them out.\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Black feminist activist Loretta Ross says, we have to call them in.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3789, \"end\": 3801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loretta_Ross\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Loretta Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loretta_Ross\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loretta_Ross\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stakes are too high for us tosit on the sidelines.\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to speak the truth.\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two plus two does not equal five.\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The emperor has no clothes.\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And drag queens at the Last Supper are not a threat to Christianity.\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 4047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4034, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 4.821257331944368e-12, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump, however, is, and he has already dragged down a large swath of evangelicals into his cult.\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now is not the time to clutch pearls.\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I imagine Jesus would have had a good laugh with the drag queens.\", \"from\": 4185, \"to\": 4250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4195, \"end\": 4200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999159758808, \"rank\": 8.402430618153063e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, keep in mind, when he had his chance to amass political power, he did not make a deal with the devil.\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Susan M. Shawis professor of women, gender and sexuality studies at Oregon State University in Corvallis, Ore. She also is an ordained Baptist minister and holds master's and doctoral degrees from Southern Baptist Theological Seminary.\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4443, \"end\": 4449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9672006809237971, \"rank\": 0.03391159605118162, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 4470, \"end\": 4479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corvallis_Knights\", \"score\": 0.9999999695401134, \"rank\": 3.0458027804097826e-08, \"text\": \"Corvallis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corvallis_Knights\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corvallis_Knights\"}, {\"begin\": 4510, \"end\": 4517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"score\": 0.9790338702261326, \"rank\": 0.02140486000940716, \"text\": \"Baptist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\"}, {\"begin\": 4572, \"end\